{"title": "Xiaomi\u2019s Mi Mix 2 may have even smaller bezels", "content": " \nThe nearly bezel-free Xiaomi Mi Mix kicked off the Great Bezel Race of 2017, and now it seems like its successor may be right around the corner. Designer Philippe Starck posted a video of what looks to be the next version of the Mi Mix on his Facebook page with the tagline \u201ceven less\u201d hinting that the device would have even smaller bezels. \n\n\n\nEven lessPosted by Starck on Thursday, August 17, 2017\n\nOutside of this short clip, we don\u2019t know much about the Mi Mix 2 yet. It should also be noted that the video is a conceptual product design, so things may change before we see the actual finished version of the smartphone. But given that the original Mi Mix was shown off last October, it shouldn't be much longer before we get details surrounding Xiaomi\u2019s next major device.\n"}
